data.description: STUNNING, well maintained 4 bdrm 3 full bth corner lot home in Langston Ridge Subdivision w/ loft and in-law suite. Open floor plan w/ GE stainless steel appliances, oversized gourmet island w cabinets for storage and granite counter tops throughout kitchen. Screened in porch plus uncovered cement pad. Great for grilling and outdoor activities. Fenced in yard. HUGE master suite w tray ceiling that sits above entire 2 car garage. Master bth w/ enclosed tile surround walk in shower w/ bench and grab bar. Garden tub and raised height double vanity. Elongated comfort height commode w/ 2 WICs. Refrigerator, washer & dryer, outdoor play gym, security system w/ ADT, and patio storage bin will convey. Community pool and clubhouse to host events. Close to shops and restaurants. Easy access to I-540 and Hwy 64. Close distance to newly remodeled Knightdale Station Park and downtown Knightdale w/ brewery and eateries. A must see!
